1
00:00:05,980 --> 00:00:16,090

2
00:00:30,860 --> 00:00:33,500
♫  Overcoming self-doubt and finding purpose  ♫

3
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:36,180
♫  Enduring the trials of life and death  ♫

4
00:00:36,180 --> 00:00:40,300
♫  As I gaze into the dark night  ♫

5
00:00:41,594 --> 00:00:44,180
♫  My spirit has not been broken  ♫

6
00:00:44,180 --> 00:00:46,820
♫  And unleash this passion  ♫

7
00:00:46,820 --> 00:00:50,990
♫  My spirit will only grow stronger  ♫

8
00:00:51,740 --> 00:00:54,760
♫  Splitting mountains and parting seas  ♫

9
00:00:54,760 --> 00:00:57,410
♫  Answering the sword's call and entering the Martial World  ♫

10
00:00:57,410 --> 00:01:02,200
♫  I'm the chosen one, fate in this turbulent world  ♫

11
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:05,440
♫  Keeping my distance from the world  ♫

12
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:08,120
♫  Who can understand my loneliness?  ♫

13
00:01:08,120 --> 00:01:11,820
♫  A single thought, gazing down  ♫

14
00:01:11,820 --> 00:01:14,540
♫  With swords drawn, frost flies through the air  ♫

15
00:01:14,540 --> 00:01:17,180
♫  With faith that conquers the world with one strike  ♫

16
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:22,320
♫  Soaring through the sky, the sword reigns everywhere  ♫

17
00:01:22,320 --> 00:01:25,140
♫  Breaking through the waves, dancing drunkenly everywhere  ♫

18
00:01:25,140 --> 00:01:27,860
♫  Protecting the people, no matter the cost  ♫

19
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:32,420
♫  Atop the peak, you and I shall battle all out  ♫

20
00:01:32,420 --> 00:01:34,500

21
00:01:39,940 --> 00:01:42,820

22
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:48,360

23
00:01:49,227 --> 00:01:52,020

24
00:01:55,860 --> 00:01:58,140
Miss. If I've calculated right,

25
00:01:58,140 --> 00:02:01,540
the White-Haired Deity and Marquis Purple Robe should have arrived at Tian Wai Tian.

26
00:02:01,540 --> 00:02:07,440
If Second Miss sees them but not you, she'll be angry.

27
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:14,380
I asked them to leave first because I wanted to visit lands that once belonged to Beique.

28
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:20,000
I'm sure Qing'er won't be mad once she hears the reason.

29
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:29,640
Young Miss, there's a house there.

30
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:37,060

31
00:02:39,180 --> 00:02:41,080
 Come in.

32
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:51,040
Sir, Xichu's Sword Song has appeared and the natural martial artist has been found.

33
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:57,320
After the Sword Deity fell, his body was hung above the city wall.

34
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:59,960
I saw it with my own eyes.

35
00:03:01,540 --> 00:03:07,360
Only Scholar Deity can pass down Xichu's Sword Song now.

36
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,960
The Scholarly Deity...

37
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:12,360
The Art of Drugs...

38
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:17,160
The revival of our country is around the corner.

39
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:22,320

40
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:45,840
Miss, the person they worship is Beique's Emperor Gouchen.

41
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:49,580
They are our subjects.

42
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:54,380
Just now... I saw the dates on your memorial tablet.

43
00:03:54,380 --> 00:03:59,160
Did your spouse and father-in-law pass away 15 years ago?

44
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:07,700
My husband and my father-in-law died in the battle between Beique and Beili 15 years ago.

45
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:13,500
 Have you ever thought maybe Beique would be rebuilt one day?

46
00:04:13,500 --> 00:04:17,100
 Even if Beique is rebuilt, so what?

47
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:25,360
My husband and my son can never come back.

48
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:30,460
When another war begins,

49
00:04:30,460 --> 00:04:38,600
how many more women will lose their husbands and children?

50
00:04:39,380 --> 00:04:44,460
 Then why should we rebuild the country?

51
00:04:48,340 --> 00:04:52,140
Miss, what's on your mind?

52
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:58,820
If we travel north for another 20 li, we'll arrive at the former capital, right?

53
00:04:58,820 --> 00:05:02,820
Every Lantern Festival would be illuminated with lanterns.

54
00:05:02,820 --> 00:05:09,120
I used to think that was the most beautiful scene in the mortal world.

55
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:17,660
But it seems like regardless of whether it's the capital of a nation,

56
00:05:17,660 --> 00:05:25,644
or if it's still run by the same person, if there are decades of peace,

57
00:05:25,644 --> 00:05:31,880
it will continue to be illuminated by lanterns during the Lantern Festival.

58
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:40,220
Life is short.

59
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:44,300
Perhaps the survivors of Beique

60
00:05:47,460 --> 00:05:55,600
don't need to rebuild Beique, but rather, peaceful moments like tonight.

61
00:06:08,580 --> 00:06:11,020
 Xichu's Sword Song's Cosmic Path.

62
00:06:11,020 --> 00:06:13,480
 Everyone respects and avoids it.

63
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,640
 Find the Sly Path so that it can be of my use.

64
00:06:15,640 --> 00:06:18,640
 But if it endangers the Baili Family, retreat.

65
00:06:21,540 --> 00:06:23,740
Father, oh, Father.

66
00:06:23,740 --> 00:06:27,020
I'd love to witness the Cosmic Path myself.

67
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,931
Father sent some news?

68
00:06:32,820 --> 00:06:36,640
He said that beneath the Cosmic Path lays the Sly Path.

69
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,660
Common people can have the Cosmic Path.

70
00:06:38,660 --> 00:06:40,700
The Sly Path is for the Wen Family.

71
00:06:40,700 --> 00:06:43,166
What is the Sly Path?

72
00:06:43,166 --> 00:06:47,286
I've only heard of it, but not seen it.

73
00:06:47,286 --> 00:06:50,686
It's said to be something regarding Xichu's Art of Drugs.

74
00:06:50,686 --> 00:06:54,286
If it exists, even the deities and ghosts fear it.

75
00:06:54,286 --> 00:06:56,866
What if we can't find it?

76
00:06:56,866 --> 00:06:58,746
I wonder about that too.

77
00:06:58,746 --> 00:07:05,086
If we can't find it, will you help the Baili Family or the Wen Family?

78
00:07:08,506 --> 00:07:11,086
I'll ask my son then.

79
00:07:11,086 --> 00:07:14,326
I'll help whoever he wants me to help.

80
00:07:16,146 --> 00:07:17,566
Don't worry.

81
00:07:17,566 --> 00:07:22,526
Father said that if it endangers the Baili Family, we back off.

82
00:07:23,206 --> 00:07:27,346
He told you to back off, but not to assist.

83
00:07:29,306 --> 00:07:33,466
It means he's noticed it's different this time.

84
00:07:36,723 --> 00:07:39,583
But Father can only represent himself. Not me.

85
00:07:39,583 --> 00:07:43,183
I don't care about the Baili Family, but I won't let anyone harm you,

86
00:07:43,183 --> 00:07:45,703
not to mention my nephew!

87
00:07:45,703 --> 00:07:47,503
Unless...

88
00:07:48,983 --> 00:07:51,223
I'm dead.

89
00:07:54,983 --> 00:07:59,543

90
00:08:24,423 --> 00:08:27,563
I wonder how Sikong Changfeng is doing now.

91
00:08:40,503 --> 00:08:44,263

92
00:09:10,323 --> 00:09:13,863

93
00:09:49,363 --> 00:09:50,763
Thank you, Senior.

94
00:09:50,763 --> 00:09:53,247
Don't rush to thank me.

95
00:09:53,247 --> 00:09:55,963
I didn't say I'd save you.

96
00:09:57,403 --> 00:10:01,003
Tell me. Did Wen Hujiu ask you to come here?

97
00:10:01,003 --> 00:10:04,483
Did he say that when I saw the poison in you,

98
00:10:04,483 --> 00:10:08,563
I'd do my best to cure you to prove that I was better than him?

99
00:10:08,563 --> 00:10:11,543
And once I fed you the antidote and your previous injuries flared up,

100
00:10:11,543 --> 00:10:14,123
I'd think it was another one of his tricks

101
00:10:14,123 --> 00:10:17,483
and still do my very best to save you.

102
00:10:17,483 --> 00:10:19,263
 Oh, no.

103
00:10:19,263 --> 00:10:22,083
 Senior Wen told me that the Medicine King would save me,

104
00:10:22,083 --> 00:10:25,783
 but he didn't tell me what to do if he saw through the plan.

105
00:10:26,343 --> 00:10:31,463
Only one person can put five poisons in a body. No one else can do it.

106
00:10:31,463 --> 00:10:35,263
Only he would try such a childish trick.

107
00:10:39,783 --> 00:10:41,783
Don't move.

108
00:10:41,783 --> 00:10:46,583
If you won't save me, then I won't stay.

109
00:10:46,583 --> 00:10:48,663
I didn't say I wouldn't save you.

110
00:10:48,663 --> 00:10:51,643
However, I have one condition.

111
00:10:52,203 --> 00:10:53,603
What is it?

112
00:10:53,603 --> 00:10:58,123
In reality, you should have been dead.

113
00:10:58,123 --> 00:10:59,843
What's kept you alive?

114
00:10:59,843 --> 00:11:03,143
Has a famous physician treated you?

115
00:11:04,263 --> 00:11:06,783
I have no money for a physician.

116
00:11:06,783 --> 00:11:13,263
I saw a book about herbs, gathered some and ingested them randomly.

117
00:11:13,263 --> 00:11:15,823
How quaint.

118
00:11:15,823 --> 00:11:18,903
You might really have a talent for medicine.

119
00:11:18,903 --> 00:11:25,143
Good. I need an apprentice to test my herbs and to serve me.

120
00:11:25,143 --> 00:11:29,763
He may follow my steps after I pass away and become a medicine king.

121
00:11:29,763 --> 00:11:35,603
You're too old to be an apprentice, but there's really no one else around here.

122
00:11:35,603 --> 00:11:37,683
I'll just have to make do.

123
00:11:37,683 --> 00:11:39,663
Farewell.

124
00:11:39,663 --> 00:11:42,303
Fine, fine. Just six months.

125
00:11:42,303 --> 00:11:46,483
Keep me company for six months and I'll save you.

126
00:11:47,543 --> 00:11:50,763
- Just six months? 
 - Yes.

127
00:11:50,763 --> 00:11:56,383
Maybe after six months, you'll want to stay.

128
00:12:03,143 --> 00:12:04,643
All right.

129
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:15,263
What's the matter?

130
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:20,243
Sir, it's Young Master Zhuomo.

131
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:25,763
Heading to Qiandong City, Feng Feng?

132
00:12:25,763 --> 00:12:30,443
I knew that with your temperament, you would rush here non-stop at once.

133
00:12:30,443 --> 00:12:34,043
And with my reasoning, I knew you'd pass by here.

134
00:12:34,043 --> 00:12:36,843
What do you think? Isn't my prediction correct?

135
00:12:36,843 --> 00:12:38,703
Compliment me.

136
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:55,103
Father.

137
00:12:55,763 --> 00:12:59,483
I have news from Tianqi City.

138
00:13:01,403 --> 00:13:04,163
It's about Little Master from the Academy.

139
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:26,820
My dear father.

140
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:29,443
The sun hasn't even come out yet. What are you doing?

141
00:13:29,443 --> 00:13:32,143
Your uncle told me that you wanted to learn swordsmanship.

142
00:13:32,143 --> 00:13:34,983
So get up and practice.

143
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:16,260
You little brat. He even falls asleep here.

144
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:18,540
How rude.

145
00:14:21,620 --> 00:14:26,060
Hold onto your sword properly. A good swordsman doesn't leave it laying around randomly.

146
00:14:26,060 --> 00:14:28,300
You're going to teach me swordsmanship?

147
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,920
Isn't it obvious?

148
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,180
I don't want you to teach me.

149
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:37,940
What? You don't think I'm good enough?

150
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:42,440
Look. What do you think of this sword?

151
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:45,420
A Celestial Level sword is naturally among the best.

152
00:14:45,420 --> 00:14:47,040
Naturally...

153
00:14:47,040 --> 00:14:52,000
If I have the best sword, I must be tutored by the greatest swordsman.

154
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:56,940
I heard the strongest individual is Mister Li from Jixia Academy in Tianqi City.

155
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:59,310
Since I can't head to Tianqi City,

156
00:14:59,310 --> 00:15:01,900
just find me someone of his caliber.

157
00:15:02,700 --> 00:15:05,060
What a brat.

158
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:33,160
Like I said, a good swordsman doesn't leave it laying around randomly.

159
00:15:33,160 --> 00:15:34,800
Give it back.

160
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:48,740
There you go. Now, use it.

161
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:50,500
Sure.

162
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:06,500
That's how you wield a sword?

163
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:09,460
- Again. 
 - Why bother?

164
00:16:09,460 --> 00:16:12,320
Learn how to draw it first.

165
00:16:14,520 --> 00:16:16,800
There you go.

166
00:17:09,300 --> 00:17:11,800
This is how you draw a sword.

167
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:15,700
This is the unsheathing technique of my Instant Kill Sword Arts.

168
00:17:15,700 --> 00:17:19,880
I could only master the basics of the sword technique my master taught me.

169
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:24,760
Yet I remember something he told me.

170
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:28,020
You must have a reason to draw your sword, and to sheathe it when you have completed your mission.

171
00:17:28,020 --> 00:17:32,000
The sword wave must be fast like lightning, yet silent.

172
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:36,700
Always know why you draw your sword.

173
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:42,260
From now on, you'll be confined to this yard.

174
00:17:42,260 --> 00:17:47,580
When your unsheathing technique is strong enough to slice this scarecrow in half,

175
00:17:47,580 --> 00:17:50,780
you can leave here.

176
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:52,940
It's just unsheathing.

177
00:17:57,660 --> 00:17:59,820
But that looked cool.

178
00:18:04,300 --> 00:18:07,600

179
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:14,240
I don't understand. Why must we wear these outfits?

180
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:17,900
Because Master said that white best suits a refined gentleman.

181
00:18:17,900 --> 00:18:21,680
And this is what a disciple of the Academy should look like.

182
00:18:22,180 --> 00:18:26,080
Unlike you, I hate white.

183
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:32,880
The point is it's too much trouble to wash it. Plus if it's stained,

184
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:38,900
isn't it the opposite of looking like a refined gentleman like Master said?

185
00:18:38,900 --> 00:18:44,800
Master knew you would complain, so he told me to tell you that this was a ritual.

186
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:47,900

187
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:56,480
You and Marquis forced Dongjun to practice swordsmanship in the backyard to avoid someone, didn't you?

188
00:18:56,980 --> 00:19:00,240
Little Master from the Academy.

189
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:06,720
Little Master isn't that person's only identity.

190
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:10,700
But a mere backyard cannot possibly hold Dongjun captive.

191
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:16,920
What if he really cuts the scarecrow in half with one slash?

192
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:23,390
Talented as he may be, he can't possible master the basics of the unsheathing skill in a few days.

193
00:19:23,390 --> 00:19:25,660
Without any internal strength as a foundation,

194
00:19:25,660 --> 00:19:28,420
even a month won't be long enough.

195
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:32,380
What if... he has internal strength?

196
00:19:35,980 --> 00:19:39,400
Hujiu, that's impossible.

197
00:19:42,860 --> 00:19:44,460
Sir.

198
00:19:44,460 --> 00:19:47,060
What's the urgency?

199
00:19:47,060 --> 00:19:49,200
Envoys from the Academy are here.

200
00:20:02,320 --> 00:20:07,180
It must be Baili Chengfeng, the son of Marquis Zhenxi.

201
00:20:07,180 --> 00:20:09,400
He's Baili Dongjun's father?

202
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:13,420
He's a powerful one.

203
00:20:16,900 --> 00:20:18,820
Heir Apparent.

204
00:20:19,660 --> 00:20:23,880
Greetings, Little Master.

205
00:20:34,540 --> 00:20:36,320
 Internal strength?

206
00:20:37,260 --> 00:20:40,200
 Why does Dongjun have internal strength?

207
00:20:40,200 --> 00:20:42,800
 He doesn't seem to be aware of it.

208
00:20:46,400 --> 00:20:50,290
Secretly, under everyone's eyes,

209
00:20:50,290 --> 00:20:56,010
using liquor brewing as a cover-up

210
00:20:56,010 --> 00:20:58,640
for cultivating internal energy...

211
00:21:01,160 --> 00:21:05,440
Perhaps this is the Sly Path Father mentioned.

212
00:21:06,660 --> 00:21:08,780
Xiao Baili.

213
00:21:10,020 --> 00:21:12,880
How long can you hide it?

214
00:22:08,740 --> 00:22:11,900
How's that? Not bad, right?

215
00:22:13,420 --> 00:22:17,820
But Young Master, this scarecrow...

216
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,900
is still the same.

217
00:22:21,900 --> 00:22:24,040
Impossible.

218
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:29,200
Why is it unaffected at all?

219
00:22:30,840 --> 00:22:32,820
That shouldn't be.

220
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:37,280
I used all my strength.

221
00:22:40,660 --> 00:22:43,300
What stupid sword is this? A Celestial Level sword?

222
00:22:43,300 --> 00:22:45,500
It can't even slash through a scarecrow.

223
00:22:45,500 --> 00:22:47,100
I'm done.

224
00:22:47,100 --> 00:22:49,920
Young Master, you can't leave now.

225
00:22:49,920 --> 00:22:52,100
After the last time, your father has begun to suspect me.

226
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:56,740
If I release you again, he'll think we conspired and we'll be found out.

227
00:22:56,740 --> 00:23:01,180
Fine. I'll stay. Ask my grandfather to rescue me.

228
00:23:01,180 --> 00:23:03,940
But he already dropped by this morning.

229
00:23:03,940 --> 00:23:06,220
Grandfather was here?

230
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:11,200
He looked at you from outside and said "not bad," before going to the camp.

231
00:23:12,740 --> 00:23:18,740
They even bought off Grandfather. Great. How infuriating!

232
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:29,260
Rui'er, tell me, what's the best way to leave this backyard?

233
00:23:31,460 --> 00:23:36,740
Knock me out and forcibly get out. Or...

234
00:23:37,820 --> 00:23:40,420
master the unsheathing skill.

235
00:23:57,120 --> 00:23:59,120
Young Master...

236
00:24:04,260 --> 00:24:06,260
It's just unsheathing a sword.

237
00:24:12,360 --> 00:24:13,900
I'll do it!

238
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:37,360
This is...

239
00:24:38,980 --> 00:24:42,260
Me? I'm also a disciple of the Academy.

240
00:24:42,260 --> 00:24:44,340
However, I'm not an envoy.

241
00:24:44,340 --> 00:24:47,220
I came to Qiandong City to meet a friend and catch up.

242
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:51,460
Heir Apparent, just pretend that I'm not here.

243
00:24:53,380 --> 00:24:56,300
This senior brother of mine comes from the Martial World.

244
00:24:56,300 --> 00:25:00,340
Please don't mind his manner of speech.

245
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:04,700
So you too, are a disciple of Mister Li.

246
00:25:04,700 --> 00:25:08,100
Stop. Please don't be scared by that old man's reputation.

247
00:25:08,100 --> 00:25:12,400
He's just an ordinary and fussy old man.

248
00:25:12,400 --> 00:25:15,300
Do you know how fussy he is? I hate wearing this thing.

249
00:25:15,300 --> 00:25:17,900
But what can I do? It's the Academy's rule.

250
00:25:17,900 --> 00:25:21,200
Heir Apparent, please, please don't be offended.

251
00:25:21,200 --> 00:25:23,100
Of course, not.

252
00:25:24,143 --> 00:25:29,163
May I know how many people you wish to take from Qiandong City?

253
00:25:32,543 --> 00:25:36,683
What if...

254
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:41,100
it's just one individual?

255
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:47,900
The Academy sure has strict requirements.

256
