357
00:37:05,286 --> 00:37:07,606
You're the remnant of Xichu.

358
00:37:07,606 --> 00:37:12,986
You must be detained and charged by the Court of Justice.

359
00:37:12,986 --> 00:37:18,846
Anyone could've done this, such as the local prefecture, the Court of Justice,

360
00:37:18,846 --> 00:37:20,966
or even the Crown Prince's Shadow Guard.

361
00:37:20,966 --> 00:37:24,806
Why you, a member of the Academy?

362
00:37:24,806 --> 00:37:29,446
You must have a unique identity.

363
00:37:29,446 --> 00:37:31,246
Your surname is Xiao.

364
00:37:31,246 --> 00:37:35,566
He asked you to come here to earn some merits

365
00:37:35,566 --> 00:37:39,686
