377
00:39:13,446 --> 00:39:15,606
My master possesses a sword technique.

378
00:39:15,606 --> 00:39:17,766
He calls it the Second-best sword technique.

379
00:39:17,766 --> 00:39:23,266
I cannot master it, nor am I strong enough to grasp it.

380
00:39:23,266 --> 00:39:27,926
